snippet.title: Life is not auto，released on Steam！
snippet.description: Today, 'Life is not auto' has finally been released! As our very first game, it's safe to say we poured our hearts and souls into it, but there are still many rough and unpolished edges. We will keep striving to improve. We hope you all enjoy it!
